title: Mac OS X Wallpapers & Screensavers Collection
description:
Mac OS X Wallpapers & Screensavers Collection for Windows


Mac OS X Wallpapers:
This collection contains all default Mac OS X wallpapers (from Jaguar, Panther, Tiger & Leopard - 104 total). All wallpapers have their default resolution: the older 1024x768 - 1280x1024 & the newer 1600x1024 - 2560x1600.

Mac OS X Screensavers:
Flurry v1.2.0.4 & Windows versions of the Slideshow Screensaver: MotionPicture v1.14.1 & Nostalgic Screensaver v1.11. Install: Copy the screensavers to your System32 directory & select and configure them in the Screensaver tab: Right click on your Desktop, select Properties, select the Screen Saver tab, secect one of the Screensavers, click on Settings and change the Picture Directory from the Slideshow screensavers to the directory where you extracted the Wallpapers.


This archive is compressed with 7-Zip - www.7-zip.org (free)
